[IG LIVE] Students Open Recruitment: Life as SC Student and How to Become One

Speakers:
1. Ayesha Felice
Peers of SCNB 3, Founder and CEO of Gores Denai and Layar Belajar, and 2022 The Diana Award Recipient
2. Fakhri Ihsan Nalendro
Students of SCNB 1, Peers of SCNB 3, President at 180DC ITS, and Ex-Deloitte
3. Firmansjah Muhammad
Director of Incubation SCNB 3, Ex-BCG & Grab
4. Jekinda Malika
Director of Growth SCNB 3, Ex-Payfazz, Grab

JOIN Whatsapp group as we will give EXCLUSIVE ANNOUNCEMENT BY TODAY: https://bit.ly/SCStudentsWAG2

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond
#studentscatalyst #SCNB3

A trip back memory lane from StudentsCatalyst National Batch 2. We are glad to have met all the outstanding students, peers and management team. 

We cannot wait to see what StudentsCatalyst will achieve next batch! Here’s to another chapter and more milestones.

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond.

#StudentsCatalyst

[SUMMIT RECAP 2022]

We are excited to share the memories of our very first Summit of StudentsCatalyst National Batch 2. We are extremely grateful for your enthusiasm that helped make this event a success!

We will see you in our next Summit.

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond.

#StudentsCatalyst

StudentsCatalyst Summit 2022!

Our Community Director & Summit Manager are here to answer all your questions and doubts regarding our upcoming biggest event: Summit! 

Worry less, here are the answers you are looking for!

Go register yourself and get the early bird ticket on bit.ly/SCSummit2022 NOW!

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond

StudentsCatalyst National Batch 2 proudly presents our biggest virtual career festival!

A place to seek your passion, maximize your potential, and to wrap it up in a real-life opportunity.

Do not miss out and quickly register yourself at https://bit.ly/SCSummit22

Early birds will get a special price for our 3 days summit! So what are you waiting for?

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond
#StudentsCatalyst

Introducing, This Year’s Biggest National Student Summit — Coming Soon! 

With the pandemic still being an ongoing challenge for the world, job markets and study opportunities are only some of the few secotrs being heavily impacted. Eventually, the country and the world will recover from the pandemic, and economic revival will create more job opportunities. This recovery is projected to transform not only the labor market, but also how the world works. 

As students and future leaders of tomorrow, are you prepared for this change? With exciting events, fairs, and socializing forums ready to cater to your future career needs and development, StudentsCatalyst is excited to announce our upcoming Summit! Continue to follow along on our journey as we empower students to network, inspire, and go beyond with us.

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond.
#StudentsCatalyst

The family of StudentsCatalyst would like to send big thanks to all of the highly motivated students in Indonesia. We’re very thrilled to announce that we received over 1400+ applicants in our second National Batch!

For applicants, we will be assesing your applications soon so make sure to check your email every once in a while! Stay tuned to more updates on our social media too.

We are very excited to meet all the students and start the journey with you. We hope to see you soon!

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond

#StudentsCatalyst

Our President & Director of Incubation is here to clear out all of your doubts and questions regarding StudentsCatalyst and the incubation program. Tune in to get all the answers you need!

Don’t forget to send in your application at
https://bit.ly/SCStudentRecruitment2
TODAY!

Network, Inspire, and Go Beyond

#StudentsCatalyst

[STUDENTS ONBOARDING: SCNB4 INCUBATION PROGRAM]

NEW JOURNEY IS STARTED!

Exclusive for SCNB 4 Incubation Program Students, we present you this remarkable meeting with our extraordinary 
speaker!
#1: Destination Discovery: Profit, Passion, and Purpose with Cania Citta as Content Creator
#2: Navigating Digital Presence through Personal Branding with Deris Nagara as Master of Public Administration Candidate 
at Columbia University, Founder and CEO of DANAYA, and Outgoing President of SIPASA Columbia University

We also invite our outstanding alumni to speak about Amplify Your Brilliance with StudentsCatalyst's
- From High Achiever Path: Calista Feroniq Gunawan as Incoming Deloitte US Audit & Assurance Intern Summer 2025 and Beasiswa Indonesia Maju (LPDP) Awardee to University of Illinois Urbana-Champaign
- From Entrepreneur Path: Jonathan Natasaputra as Research Analyst at PT. Adhi Beton Persada and Ex-CEO Office Analyst at Fairatmos
- From Organization Path: Hawraul Insiyyah as Ex-Campaign Marketing Intern at Grab and Ex-Project Consultant at Procter 
& Gamble (P&G)

Mark your calendars for Saturday, 20th January 2024, from 08.00 to 15.30 WIB via Zoom Meeting. This exclusive onboarding event is tailored just for you, SCNB 4 Incubation Program Students.

Let's kick off your academic journey 
together with a spirit of curiosity and collaboration!
#SCNB4 #StudentsIncubation #BCG #Scholarship #Organization #Presiden #LPDP

[ ACADEMIC PARTNER REVEAL #7: DELOITTE ]

Hello, Highly-Motivated Students in Indonesia! 
Eagerly awaiting the introduction of our next academic partner? We're pleased to present Deloitte to you.

Deloitte, acknowledged as a top consulting service by reputable institutions such as Gartner, IDC MarketScape, Forrester, and ALM, is an ideal fit for our StudentsCatalyst Incubation Program. Their consistent excellence across various markets and prominent revenue position makes them a valuable contributor to the case competition, offering invaluable real-world expertise and insights.

Get prepared for the next exciting partner? Stay tuned for the big reveal!
